  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180°C (350°F).",
    "Combine spring water, all-purpose flour, tart oil, and fresh thyme in a bowl.",
    "Roll out dough to a thickness of 5mm (1/5 inch).",
    "Transfer dough to a tart pan with a removable bottom.",
    "Bake crust for 20 minutes or until lightly golden.",
    "In a blender, puree kiwifruit, granulated sugar, and lemon juice until smooth.",
    "Pour kiwifruit compote into the baked tart crust.",
    "Bake for an additional 20 minutes or until filling is set.",
    "Let cool completely before serving."
